AND (dered_r-dered_i) < # AND (dered_r-dered_i) > # AND (dered_g-dered_r) < # AND (dered_g-dered_r) > # AND cmodelmag_i-extinction_i BETWEEN # AND # AND fiber2mag_i < # INTO micado_galaxies_loRG
